{"tid":1992041,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"信報：保皇已準備好出招 但要等埋大口狗揾咗法律意見先","createTime":"2020-04-28T02:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T03:45:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dc3abda55540e4212b871e9bb992488252e65e8f","tid":1992041,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:00:20.000Z","msg":"然而，在兩辦發聲後已接連進行兩次內委會會議，選舉主席進度卻無明顯加快。建制派「副班長」陳克勤在上次會議後僅稱，各種方案已準備妥當，隨時可以「出招」，但要等待梁君彥徵詢相關法律意見.....<br />\n<br />\n有建制派人士透露......上述「各種方案」皆有局限......即使根據《基本法》79條，以違反立法會誓言動議譴責郭榮鏗，也難湊夠法定所需的三分之二議員通過議案；再次修改《議事規則》亦遠水難救近火。<br />\n<br />\n建制派中人直言.....內會癱瘓令法案無法交上大會恢復二讀和三讀，意味徵收一手樓空置稅及禁電子煙等修例將一拖再拖，隨時到下屆立法會重頭來過，對某些建制功能界別議員而言不無着數。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2448024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2448024&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=775e90c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2448024</a>"},{"pid":"ffcfd65fda6c3db29302529a968c31bdb10085d2","tid":1992041,"uid":6604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"保蝗黨各懷鬼胎"},{"pid":"e796a706f6cf701ded67653b37da5b87b1587dc2","tid":1992041,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:03:31.000Z","msg":"石禮謙想過空置税？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a90a9ba7461c8523d69806d064cf79f8bc1e28","tid":1992041,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:05:50.000Z","msg":"空置稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到咁撚正義唔撚提支歌法？"},{"pid":"c9c42e5528207ab5a609f336a67c257c18b4eeaa","tid":1992041,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f